Package: libsafec
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Safe C Library
 The Safe C Library provides secure string and memory functions to
 prevent buffer overflows and other security vulnerabilities.

Package: libsafec-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libsafec (= ${version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Safe C Library - development files
 The Safe C Library provides secure string and memory functions to
 prevent buffer overflows and other security vulnerabilities.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static library.

Package: safec-utils
Architecture: any
Section: utils
Depends: libsafec (= ${version}), perl, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Safe C Library - API checker utility
 The Safe C Library provides secure string and memory functions to
 prevent buffer overflows and other security vulnerabilities.
 .
 This package contains the check_for_unsafe_apis utility.
